Dear LTS Participants,<br><br>

We're looking forward to welcoming you to our Learn to Scull program ({{ page.lts_program_number }}) starting tomorrow, {{ page.session_dates[0] | split: '(' | first | strip }} at {{ page.session_start_time | default: "8:30 AM" }}. Please arrive by {{ page.arrival_time | default: "8:20 AM" }} at {{ page.meeting_location | default: "the main entrance of Beal Community Boathouse at Bandemer Park" }}.<br><br>

**Final Checklist**<br><br>
✓ USRowing Learn-to-Row membership ($10) - required for insurance<br>
✓ AARC waiver completed online<br>
