**What to Bring**<br><br>
- **Warm layers** - snug athletic clothes (no baggy items that catch in tracks). Dress for 55-60°F + wind!<br>
- Water bottle (32 oz recommended)<br>
- Sunscreen, hat & sunglasses<br>
- **Towel & full change of clothes** - you'll get wet during flip test, and cool + windy conditions make this essential<br><br>

**Quick Reminders**<br><br>
- Program runs {{ page.session_time | default: "8:30 - 11:30 AM" }} both days (tomorrow & Sunday)<br>
